com.github.nosan.embedded.cassandra

Class DataStaxCassandra

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.nosan.embedded.cassandra.Cassandra
      • com.github.nosan.embedded.cassandra.DataStaxCassandra

  • public class DataStaxCassandra
extends Cassandra
    Cassandra extension which adds functionality not only to start Apache Cassandra, but a Cluster creation as well.

    The typical usage is: 

     public class CassandraTests {
 private final static DataStaxCassandra cassandra = new DataStaxCassandra();
 @BeforeClass
 public static void start() {
 cassandra.start();
 }
 @Test
 public void test() {
 Session session = cassandra.getSession();
 //
 }
 @AfterClass
 public static void stop() {
 cassandra.stop();
 }
 }
    Author:
    Dmytro Nosan
    See Also:
    Cassandra, CqlScriptUtils
